Package: qvivid
Title: Fast Quantum Simulation and Vivid Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = c("Sanmi", "(Oluwasanmi)"),
      family = "Adenaiye",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
      email = "dradenaiyesanmi@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Description: Builds, simulates, inspects, and animates gate-based quantum
    circuits in R. The package provides reference and compiled statevector
    backends, reproducible shot sampling, circuit diagrams, phase-aware state
    plots, reduced-state Bloch spheres, journal-sized figure export, and
    animated trajectories.
